title: State owed millions by politicians and political organizations for filing finance reports late, or not filing reports at all - What'sUpNewp
content: State owed millions by politicians and political organizations for filing finance reports late, or not filing reports at all  What'sUpNewp
description: - Advertisement -More than a hundred politicians and political organizations owe the state Board of Elections nearly $5.4 million after failing to file financial election reports or filing them late.
